sketch.compiler.dataflow.nodesToSB

Class ProduceBooleanFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FEReplacer
      • sketch.compiler.passes.lowering.SymbolTableVisitor
        • sketch.compiler.dataflow.PartialEvaluator
          • sketch.compiler.dataflow.nodesToSB.ProduceBooleanFunctions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor

    public class ProduceBooleanFunctions
extends PartialEvaluator
    This class translates the ast into a boolean function which is output to a file. The format is suitable for the SBitII backend solver.
    Preconditions:
    Arrays
    * Only 1 dimensional arrays allowed.
    * The [] operator can only be used on an array variable.
    * binary operators work only for scalars.
    * Array to array assignments are supported. (arr1 = arr2)
    * Array ranges with len != 1 are not supported.
    * Scalar to array assignments are supported.
    Author:
    asolar
